metrics.name: ProductATS_getBySkuSet
metrics.sql: select t0.id, t0.sku, t0.brand, t0.stocklevel, t0.audit_history, t0.created_at, t0.updated_at from product_ats t0 where t0.sku = any(?)

metrics.name: ProductATS_withAllProductATS
metrics.sql: select t0.id, t0.sku, t0.brand, t0.stocklevel, t0.audit_history, t0.created_at, t0.updated_at from product_ats t0 where updated_at >= ? and (t0.brand = ?) limit 1000

metrics.name: ProductATS_withAllProductATS
metrics.sql: select t0.id, t0.sku, t0.brand, t0.stocklevel, t0.audit_history, t0.created_at, t0.updated_at from product_ats t0 where updated_at >= ? and (t0.brand = ?) limit 1000 offset 1000
